被懷疑的微行星，{{link-en|WD 1145+017 b|WD 1145+017 b}}<ref name=EPeu />，其軌道週期為4.5小時， 位於會被母恆星[[洛希極限|撕裂]]的距離內，所以應該是在這顆恆星成為白矮星之前的前行星殘骸。這是第一次觀察到受到白矮星影響的行星[[潮汐力|碎片]]，在軌道上也還看見一些其它的大碎片。所有的碎片，無論大小，其軌道週期都在4.5至4.9小時之間。在恆星的光譜中顯示，岩石的物質正落到恆星上。這個系統是在[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]擴展的''K2''任務中發現的。雖然，這個系統不是一個感興趣的目標，但它是在觀測的視野中，而在對觀測到的資料進行分析時，發現了這個系統<ref name=Discovery-2015-10-21>{{cite news |url= http://news.discovery.com/space/astronomy/caught-in-the-act-white-dwarf-is-killing-a-planet-151021.htm |title= Caught in the Act: White Dwarf is Killing a Planet |date= 21 October 2015 |author= Ian O'Neill |publisher= [[Discovery_Channel|Discovery Channel]] |accessdate= 2015-11-25 |archive-date= 2016-03-10 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160310014642/http://news.discovery.com/space/astronomy/caught-in-the-act-white-dwarf-is-killing-a-planet-151021.htm }}</ref><ref name=NatGeo-2015-10-21>{{cite news |url= http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2015/10/151021-zombie-dead-star-eats-asteroid-astronomy/ |title= Zombie Star Caught Feasting On Asteroids |author= Michael D. Lemonick |date= 21 October 2015 |publisher= National Geographic |accessdate= 2015-11-25 |archive-date= 2015-10-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151024081958/http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2015/10/151021-zombie-dead-star-eats-asteroid-astronomy/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name=SciNews-2015-10-22>{{cite news |url= http://www.sci-news.com/astronomy/science-kepler-wd-1145-017-white-dwarf-03366.html |title= NASA’s Kepler K2 Mission Discovers Planet-Destroying White Dwarf Star |date= 22 October 2015 |publisher= Sci-News.com |accessdate= 2015-11-25 |archive-date= 2022-04-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20220411073618/http://www.sci-news.com/astronomy/science-kepler-wd-1145-017-white-dwarf-03366.html }}</ref><ref name=S&T-2015-10-26>{{cite news |url= http://www.skyandtelescope.com/astronomy-news/white-dwarf-eats-planet2610201523/ |title= White Dwarf Eats Mini Planet? |author= Camille M. Carlisle |date= 26 October 2015 |publisher= Sky and Telescope |accessdate= 2015-11-25 |archive-date= 2019-08-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190805012901/https://www.skyandtelescope.com/astronomy-news/white-dwarf-eats-planet2610201523/ }}</ref>。

超量的[[紅外線|紅外線輻射]]顯示它有一個溫度為{{convert|1150|K|C}} [[星周盤|星周盤]] <ref name=croll/>，來自[[錢德拉X射線天文台|錢卓太空望遠鏡]]的觀測資料發現WD 1145+017有塵埃碎片，也支持此一結果<ref name="arXiv-20170924">{{cite journal |last1=Rappaport |first1=S. |last2=Gary |first2=B.L. |last3=Vanderburg |first3=A. |last4=Xu |first4=S. |last5=Pooley |first5=D. |last6=Mukai |first6=K. |title=WD 1145+017: Optical Activity During 2016-2017 and Limits on the X-Ray Flux |url=https://arxiv.org/pdf/1709.08195.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |date=24 September 2017 |arxiv=1709.08195v1 |class=astro-ph.EP |accessdate=26 September 2017 |journal= |archive-date=2017-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926235711/https://arxiv.org/pdf/1709.08195.pdf }}</ref>。

